dsDescriptionValue.value: All Cockroach Photos taken during the study. File Names are Day#-A#, Day#-S#, and Day#-U#. Day = Day of Observation post leg removal. A = autotomy groups. U = unsterilized coxa-cut group. S = sterilized coxa-cut group. Number after letter is to identify different cockroaches. Note Day03, Day10, and Day20 have rulers in the photos for calibration. After Day 20, the microscope was improved and all photos have a built-in calibration mark that measures 10 mm by 1 mm.
